description:
Chhiartu : Maruati Singson
Lettu : Lalnuntluanga Ralte

Avocado Thatna 12-te

Avocado hi thei danglam tak mai a ni a.
Thei tam zawk chuan carbohydrates an pai a, mahse avocado erawh hi chuan thau hrisel tak a pai a. 
Zirna tam takte chuan hriselna atan a thatzia a sawi. 
Science lam zirchianna atanga avocado thatna 12-te i lo en ang. 

1. Avocado chuan nutrients a ngah hle. 
2. Balhla aiin Potassium an pai hnem zawk. 
3. Avocado hian lung tihriseltu thau tha (mono unsaturated-fatty acid) chu a pai hnem hle. 
4. Avocado-te hi fiber pai hnem tak an ni. 
5. Avocado hian cholesterol leh tri-glycerides awmzat chu a tihniam thei a ni.
6. Avocado eite hi an hrisel zawk tlangpui.
7. An thau paite chuan Thlai chaw atanga chakna hip thei turin a pui thei che a ni.
8. Avocado hian kan mitte veng theitu antioxidants chak tak mai a pai hnem hle a ni.
9. Avocado hian cancer laka inven theihna hmanrua a nei.
10. Avocado tihkhal chuan Arthritis natna lo lanchhuahna-te chu a tikiam thei a ni.
11. Avocado eina hian I rihna a tihniam thei a ni.
12. Avocado hi a tui a, ei leh inah telh a awl hle a ni. 

A pumpuia khaikhawmnaah chuan, Avocado hi chaw tha em em niin, chakna tam tak a pai a, ei leh in danga awm lo tam tak thil tha a pai a.

Rihna tihhniam nana tangkai an ni a, lung hriselna atan a tha a, a a tui hle bawk.
